# Factory CI evidence (regenerated locally and on the runner; never tracked)
# The gate-summary is a detached artefact: it is regenerated against the
# committed tree and then archived as part of the PR/CI run.  Tracking it
# would create a self-reference (the file would carry the hash of the tree
# that contains itself) and would invalidate the tree-OID binding.
